---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CaneToadFL"
  description="Privacy policy for CaneToadFL. Learn what data we collect, how we use it, and how homeowner lead information is handled."
>
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>This policy explains how CaneToadFL collects, uses, and shares information submitted through this website.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Contact information submitted through forms (name, phone, email, address/zip).</li>
      <li>Basic usage data collected through analytics tools.</li>
      <li>Lead submission metadata needed for service matching and support.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To connect homeowners with local removal providers.</li>
      <li>To improve website performance and user experience.</li>
      <li>To communicate about submitted requests.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How Lead Data Is Shared</h2>
    <p>Lead information may be shared with one or more partner providers serving your area so they can follow up about requested services.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use reasonable administrative and technical safeguards to protect submitted information. No method of transmission or storage is guaranteed to be completely secure.</p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <p>You can request updates or deletion of your submitted contact information by emailing us.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email privacy requests to: privacy@canetoadfl.com</p>
    <p>For general support, visit <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
